tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE healthcare_equity (
  patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  patient_age INT,
  patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
  inclusion_program_id UUID,
  inclusion_program_name VARCHAR(100),
  inclusion_program_description TEXT,
  inclusion_start_date DATE,
  inclusion_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Diversity_Programs (
	diversity_program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	program_name VARCHAR(255),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE,
	impact_on_outcomes VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Patient_Outcomes (
	patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	patient_name VARCHAR(255),
	diagnosis VARCHAR(255),
	treatment VARCHAR(255),
	outcome VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    gender VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    health_condition VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE diversity_programs (
    program_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    program_description VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    program_start_date DATE NOT NULL,
